ses, postings to the Emergency Information Web page , and recorded announcements left on the emergency information line at (312) 413-9696.  Emergency Contact Information   We encourage you to update the emergency contact information in your student record so campus officials can get in touch with the appropriate people quickly and easily in the case of an emergency situation.  To update your emergency contact information online:   Go to my.UIC.edu .  Log in with your netID and password.  Select the “Academics” tab, then select “Records.”  Select “Change your Emergency Contact Information including Mental Health Contact and Primary Contact if Missing.”  Select the “Emergency Contacts” and then “New Contact” to add your emergency contact information for each person.   Startel Emergency Phones on Campus  There are over 1,000 Startel emergency phones on campus; they are easily identified as 8-foot blue light poles. The red call button activates an alarm and flashing light and immediately connects you to UIC Police.  UIC SAFE app  The UIC SAFE app is a a free personal security tool that provides users with added safety on campus. Features include Friend Virtual Walk, which enables you to share your location with friends and family in real-time while walking, as well as direct and easy contact with dispatchers and first responders in case of emergencies.  SafeWalk Police/Student Patrol Escort  Students can call (312) 996-2830 to request an escort to walk them to their campus destination.  UIC Night Ride  UIC offers students and staff a nighttime transportation service, UIC Night Ride , that will pick up and drop off riders within a specific coverage area in and around the campus. All riders need a valid UIC i-card to board. The service operates 365 days a year, daily between 11 p.m. – 7 a.m.  To request a ride, call (312) 996-6800. You can also download and use the TransLōc Rider app to request rides from your mobile device. The average wait time is 15 minutes during the week and 30 minutes during the weekend.  UIC Police Phone Numbers  UIC Policy Emergency: (312) 355-5555 UIC Police Non-emergency: (312) 996-2830         Have a question? Chat live with Summer Session Staff!      Help desk software                UIC in the summer                        Links Contact Us  Sign up for E-mail Reminders  UIC Extended Campus  UIC Home  Disability Resources  Privacy Policy  Emergency Information    Loading      Have a question?  Give us a call, we can help! 312-996-9099     2016 University of Illinois at Chicago        php
